            "text": "-year-old man would have been born in the 1941/1942 year range, so finding a 1941 Chevy Pickup truck in 2021 must have seemed like destiny. This started in early November, according to the Pennsylvania State Police Department at Dublin. According to the agency, “an unknown actor (who) falsely identified themselves as a white, non-Hispanic male, who was selling an antique motor vehicle online.”",
